## Tasks

| Command | Action |
|---|---|
| `/adb` | Device status overview — connected devices, app info, memory |
| `/adb logcat [tag or package]` | Filtered logcat with crash detection |
| `/adb profile <package>` | CPU, memory, frame rate snapshot |
| `/adb db <package>` | Pull and inspect SQLite databases |
| `/adb network <package>` | Inspect network traffic via HTTP proxy |
| `/adb screenshot` | Capture and pull screenshot |
| `/adb record [duration]` | Record screen video (default 30s) |
| `/adb install <apk>` | Install APK with grant-all-permissions |
| `/adb clear <package>` | Clear app data and cache |
| `/adb deep-link <url>` | Fire deep link intent |

