## Device Management

```bash
# List connected devices with human-readable info
adb devices -l

# Target specific device for all subsequent commands
export ANDROID_SERIAL=<serial>

# Get device properties
adb shell getprop ro.build.version.release    # Android version
adb shell getprop ro.product.model            # Device model
adb shell getprop ro.build.fingerprint        # Full fingerprint

# Screen information
adb shell wm size
adb shell wm density

# Battery state (useful for CI — ensure device is charged)
adb shell dumpsys battery | grep -E "level|status|powered"
```

