## App Inspection

```bash
# Full package info: version, permissions, install time, APK path
adb shell dumpsys package <package.name>

# List all installed packages
adb shell pm list packages -f | grep <keyword>

# Get current foreground activity
adb shell dumpsys activity activities | grep mResumedActivity

# App memory breakdown
adb shell dumpsys meminfo <package.name>

# Force-stop app (respects lifecycle)
adb shell am force-stop <package.name>

# Clear app data + cache (equivalent to Settings → Clear Data)
adb shell pm clear <package.name>

# Revoke a runtime permission
adb shell pm revoke <package.name> android.permission.CAMERA
# Grant a runtime permission
adb shell pm grant <package.name> android.permission.CAMERA
```

