## Performance Profiling

```bash
# Frame rendering — identify jank (>16ms frames = dropped)
adb shell dumpsys gfxinfo <package.name>

# Detailed frame stats (last 120 frames)
adb shell dumpsys gfxinfo <package.name> framestats

# Reset gfxinfo counters before profiling
adb shell dumpsys gfxinfo <package.name> reset

# CPU usage for package
adb shell top -p $(adb shell pidof -s <package.name>) -n 1

# Memory — track over time (run repeatedly)
adb shell dumpsys meminfo <package.name> | grep -E "TOTAL|Heap|Native"

# Startup time — cold start (kill first)
adb shell am force-stop <package.name>
adb shell am start -W -n <package.name>/.<MainActivity>
# Look for: TotalTime= (full start) and WaitTime=

# Battery attribution
adb shell dumpsys batterystats --charged <package.name>
```

