## Database Access

```bash
# Pull the entire app databases directory
adb shell "run-as <package.name> cp -r /data/data/<package.name>/databases /sdcard/tmp_db"
adb pull /sdcard/tmp_db ./local_db && adb shell rm -rf /sdcard/tmp_db

# Query a specific table directly on device
adb shell "run-as <package.name> sqlite3 /data/data/<package.name>/databases/<db_name>.db 'SELECT * FROM users LIMIT 20;'"

# List all tables
adb shell "run-as <package.name> sqlite3 /data/data/<package.name>/databases/<db_name>.db '.tables'"

# Pull SharedPreferences XML
adb shell "run-as <package.name> cat /data/data/<package.name>/shared_prefs/<prefs_name>.xml"

# Pull all shared prefs
adb shell "run-as <package.name> cp -r /data/data/<package.name>/shared_prefs /sdcard/tmp_prefs"
adb pull /sdcard/tmp_prefs .
```

