## Screenshot and Screen Recording

```bash
# Screenshot — pull to current directory
adb shell screencap -p /sdcard/screen.png && adb pull /sdcard/screen.png ./screen_$(date +%H%M%S).png && adb shell rm /sdcard/screen.png

# Screen record (max 3 minutes per recording; use --time-limit)
adb shell screenrecord --time-limit 30 /sdcard/demo.mp4
adb pull /sdcard/demo.mp4 ./demo_$(date +%Y%m%d_%H%M%S).mp4
adb shell rm /sdcard/demo.mp4

# Higher bitrate for clearer recording
adb shell screenrecord --bit-rate 8000000 --time-limit 30 /sdcard/demo.mp4
```

