## Deep Links and Intent Firing

```bash
# Fire a deep link
adb shell am start -a android.intent.action.VIEW -d "myapp://profile/123"

# Start activity directly
adb shell am start -n <package.name>/.<TargetActivity>

# Start with extras (useful for debugging feature flags)
adb shell am start -n <package.name>/.<TargetActivity> \
  --es "userId" "abc123" \
  --ez "debugMode" "true"

# Broadcast an intent
adb shell am broadcast -a com.example.MY_ACTION

# Simulate low memory warning
adb shell am send-trim-memory <package.name> COMPLETE
```

