## Network Inspection

```bash
# Redirect app traffic through local proxy (e.g., Charles on 8888)
adb shell settings put global http_proxy 192.168.1.100:8888

# Remove proxy
adb shell settings delete global http_proxy

# Open port forwarding — expose device port on host (e.g., for MCP SDK)
adb forward tcp:8080 tcp:8080

# Reverse port forward — expose host port on device
adb reverse tcp:3000 tcp:3000

# Check open sockets on device
adb shell ss -tnp | grep <package.name_pid>
```

