## File System

```bash
# Push file to app's private storage (requires run-as)
adb push ./test_data.json /sdcard/test_data.json
adb shell "run-as <package.name> cp /sdcard/test_data.json /data/data/<package.name>/files/"

# List app files
adb shell "run-as <package.name> ls -la /data/data/<package.name>/"

# Pull crash logs from device
adb pull /data/tombstones/ ./tombstones/
```

